headline: Goldman Sachs upgrades AutoZone to Buy, lifts Genuine Parts to Neutral
summary: Investing.com -- Goldman Sachs upgraded AutoZone (NYSE: AZO) to Buy from Neutral and Genuine Parts (NYSE: GPC) to Neutral from Sell in a note on Thursday, citing improved risk/reward profiles for both auto parts retailers after recent market moves.
